# рџ“ќ Blog App вЂ” Full Stack Web Application

A full-stack blog platform built with **Node.js, Express, MongoDB** and a **vanilla HTML/CSS/JS** frontend. Supports user authentication, blog post management, commenting, and a separate admin dashboard for content moderation.

---

## вњЁ Features

- рџ”ђ User signup, login & JWT-based authentication
- рџ“ќ Create, read, and delete blog posts
- рџ’¬ Comment system on posts
- рџ›ЎпёЏ Admin dashboard to manage users, posts and comments
- рџ‘¤ Role-based access control (user / admin)
- рџ“± Responsive UI with vanilla HTML, CSS & JavaScript

---

## рџЏ—пёЏ Tech Stack

| Layer | Technology |
|---|---|
| Frontend | HTML, CSS, JavaScript |
| Backend | Node.js, Express.js |
| Database | MongoDB |
| Auth | JWT (JSON Web Tokens) |

